name: Crochet Chain Cuff Bracelets - Set of 3 - Salmon, Yellow, Soft Baby Blue
description:
This listing is for a set of 3 crochet chain bracelets. Light and breathable in warmer weather too!

You love to wear bracelets but sometimes they just get in the way? Trying to type on the keyboard but your bracelet keeps hitting the keyboard or worse, hitting that bumpy bone on your wrist?? 

These crochet cuffs are a nice alternative to wear something fun on your wrist but are lightweight, soft, cozy and eye catching. Consider it a cushion for your wrist when sitting at your work desk with your hand constantly on the mouse. 

Materials are a mix of wool, acrylic and cotton so there is some stretch to the material. Inside diameter of the bracelets are about 4 inches.

For best care, hand wash with soap.

name: Lenore Lady Skeleton Necklace - Victorian Gothic Lolita
description:

"Wretches! ye loved her for her wealth and hated her for her pride,
And when she fell in feeble health, ye blessed her- that she died!
How shall the ritual, then, be read?- the requiem how be sung
By you- by yours, the evil eye,- by yours, the slanderous tongue
That did to death the innocence that died, and died so young?"
~Lenore by Edgar Allen Poe~
